02:05.926 --> 02:07.561
"That you are‐‐"

02:07.594 --> 02:09.329
"That you are the winners
of a state of the art

02:09.362 --> 02:10.496
double door refrigerator."

02:10.531 --> 02:11.565
Yes.

02:13.299 --> 02:14.467
(Balki)
'"Refrigerator..'

02:14.501 --> 02:17.738
"...or a free trip for two

02:17.771 --> 02:21.675
to ex‐ci‐ting Las Vegas."

02:23.476 --> 02:24.545
Now, we are so happy

